<ab> <title>CXXIIII.  ADVERSVS CLAVDIANVM DE MVLABVS. </title> </ab>
          <l n="1"><milestone unit="para"/>Hic uolucrem Rhodani torrentis respice natam  </l>
            <l n="2">Sermonum frenis <choice><sic>snbdere</sic><corr>subdere</corr></choice> colla tuis.  </l>
            <l n="3">Iussa <choice><sic>nolat</sic><corr>uolat</corr></choice> <choice><sic>nerbis</sic><corr>uerbis</corr></choice> et uerbis iussa quiescit,  </l>
            <l n="4">Cuius captiuum est auribus arbitrium.  </l>
            <l n="5"><choice><sic>Vincnla</sic><corr>Vincula</corr></choice> sentiret, ni <choice><sic>nocis</sic><corr>uocis</corr></choice> stricta lupatis  </l>
            <l n="6">Perderet auditu <choice><sic>lnxuriam</sic><corr>luxuriam</corr></choice> generis.  </l>
            <l n="7">Cum stimulos clamor mentitur, clamor habenas,  </l>
            <l n="8">Obsequium linguae libera membra ferunt.  </l>
            <l n="9">Non opus est loris, sed nexus certa loquendi  </l>
            <l n="10">Dura catenati rostra ligat pecudis.  </l> 

          

